data.description: Immaculate one-owner home for the most discriminating buyer. Located on premium oversized corner lot with view of pond. Meticulously maintained, home features high-end upgrades including a backyard oasis with heated spa-pool, stained-stamped concrete wrap around patio & attached storage room. Inside features engineered hardwood flooring, newer AC in 2017, 3 inch plantation shutters throughout, single-piece granite island, and beautiful architectural features. Spacious master suite has bay window with view, dual shower with stone floor, dual vanities and huge walk in closet. Garages have poly-coated floors, 3rd bay is insulated with heat and ac. New roof in July. Too many extras to list-MUST SEE!
